sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Platform
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as training-operator<br/>Controller
    participant Pods as Training Pods<br/>(per-replica)
    participant HeadlessSvc as Headless Services<br/>(pod discovery)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Pods: Flow 1: Training Job Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: CREATE PyTorchJob/TFJob/...<br/>Auth: Bearer token / client cert
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-kubeflow-org-v1-*<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS (auto-rotated)<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (Allow/Deny)

    Note over Controller: Informer receives watch event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET/LIST training job CRs<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Training Job spec

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE Pods (per-replica)<br/>with framework env vars<br/>(TF_CONFIG, WORLD_SIZE, MASTER_ADDR)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE Headless Service<br/>(ClusterIP: None)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Service created

    opt Gang Scheduling Enabled
        Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE PodGroup CR<br/>(Volcano or scheduler-plugins)
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: PodGroup created
    end

    opt PyTorch Elastic Training
        Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE HorizontalPodAutoscaler<br/>(autoscaling/v2)
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: HPA created
    end

    Note over Pods,HeadlessSvc: Distributed Training Communication

    Pods->>HeadlessSvc: DNS lookup for peer pods
    HeadlessSvc-->>Pods: Pod IP addresses
    Pods->>Pods: Framework-specific communication<br/>(TCP, cluster-internal, no encryption)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: UPDATE status<br/>(Running/Succeeded/Failed)

    Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 2: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>No auth (cluster-internal)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Job lifecycle counters<br/>(created, deleted, successful,<br/>failed, restarted)
